<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We talked a lot last year about <a href=3D"htt=
ps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34031994.258404/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu=
Ymxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDgtMjEvZXZlcnlvbmUtd2FudHM=
tYS1waWVjZS1vZi1zY3VscHRvcj9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMTE3MjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaX=
