 #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; borde=
r-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc=
;"> signed with JetBlue</a>. (=E2=80=9CSpirit Had No Choice But Heed Invest=
ors and Jilt Frontier,=E2=80=9D wrote my Bloomberg Opinion colleague <a hre=
f=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34031994.258404/aHR0cHM6=
Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDctMjcvc3Bpcml0LWZ=
vcmNlZC10by1saXN0ZW4tdG8taW52ZXN0b3JzLWFuZC1kdW1wLWZyb250aWVyP2NtcGlkPUJCRD=
AxMTcyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJ=
