ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">structure</a>,=E2=
=80=9D or =E2=80=9Cstructured equity.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Gil=
lian Tan <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34031994.=
258404/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDEtMTIv=
